chart.description: percentile distributions across all active hosts
chart.name: CPU %
chart.programText:
A = data('CpuUtilization', filter=filter('oci_namespace', 'oci_computeagent')).min().publish(label='A')
C = data('CpuUtilization', filter=filter('oci_namespace', 'oci_computeagent')).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C')
D = data('CpuUtilization', filter=filter('oci_namespace', 'oci_computeagent')).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D')
E = data('CpuUtilization', filter=filter('oci_namespace', 'oci_computeagent')).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E')
F = data('CpuUtilization', filter=filter('oci_namespace', 'oci_computeagent')).max().publish(label='F')

chart.name: Hosts with Agent Installed
chart.programText:
A = data('CpuUtilization').max(over='1h').max(by=['oci_dim_resourceDisplayName']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('cpu.utilization').max(over='1h').dimensions(aliases={'oci_dim_resourceDisplayName':'host'}).max(by=['oci_dim_resourceDisplayName']).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A+B).publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (A).count().publish(label='D', enable=False)
E = (B).count().publish(label='E', enable=False)
F = (C).count().publish(label='F', enable=True)

chart.name: Disk Metrics 24h Change %
chart.programText:
A = data('DiskIopsRead', filter=filter('oci_namespace', 'oci_computeagent')).delta().sum().mean(over='1h').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('DiskIopsWritten', filter=filter('oci_namespace', 'oci_computeagent')).delta().sum().mean(over='1h').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = data('DiskBytesRead').delta().sum().mean(over='1h').publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = data('DiskBytesWritten').delta().sum().mean(over='1h').publish(label='D', enable=False)
E = (A).timeshift('1d').publish(label='E', enable=False)
F = (A/E-1).scale(100).publish(label='F')
G = (B).timeshift('1d').publish(label='G', enable=False)
H = (B/G-1).scale(100).publish(label='H')
I = (C).timeshift('1d').publish(label='I', enable=False)
J = (C/I-1).scale(100).publish(label='J')
K = (D).timeshift('1d').publish(label='K', enable=False)
L = (D/K-1).scale(100).publish(label='L')

chart.name: Network Bytes In vs.24h Change
chart.programText:
B = data('NetworksBytesIn', filter=filter('oci_namespace', 'oci_computeagent')).delta().mean(by=['oci_dim_resourceId', 'oci_dim_resourceDisplayName']).sum().publish(label='B')
C = (B).mean(over='1h').publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (C).timeshift('1d').publish(label='D', enable=False)
E = (C/D-1).scale(100).publish(label='E')
